---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	requireAuth
	title="About - Matthew Windham"
	description="A little about Matthew Windham, DevOps engineer in Austin, Texas."
>
	<main class="wrap">
		<div class="about-head">
			<img class="avatar" src="/avatar.jpg" width="140" height="140" alt="Matthew Windham" />
			<h1>About</h1>
		</div>

		<section class="bio">
			<p>
				I was born in Fort Worth, Texas, but my family moved to western Montana when I was three —
				so I claim Montana. We settled in Kalispell the summer before fourth grade, and that's
				where I grew up. Western Montana has a way of getting into you: winters on the slopes
				snowboarding, summers hiking, fly fishing, rafting, and boating, with golf mixed in
				whenever the weather allowed. It's a hard place to leave, and an easy one to miss.
			</p>
			<p>
				I went to the University of Montana and studied geology. Eventually I needed to actually
				start a career, and an opportunity came up at Cummings Electrical to get into IT. Turned
				out I liked it — and the deeper I got, the more it pulled me in. Systems, automation,
				infrastructure: it clicked in a way geology never quite did. I've been building on it ever
				since, moving from sysadmin to SRE to where I am now as a DevOps engineer.
			</p>
			<p>
				I met my wife in Dallas, and we came down to Austin together to start our life here — dog
				included. When I'm not at a screen you'll find me at Zilker Park, on a golf course, or
				working through Austin's very long list of good restaurants. Texas wasn't exactly part of
				the plan, but Austin has a way of keeping people.
			</p>
			<blockquote>
				"If a human operator needs to touch your system during normal operations, you have a bug.
				The definition of normal changes as your systems grow."
				<cite>— Carla Geisser, Google SRE</cite>
			</blockquote>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-head {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.75rem;
		padding-top: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.avatar {
		width: 140px;
		height: 140px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 153, 0, 0.35);
		box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(255, 153, 0, 0.12);
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.bio p {
		color: var(--text-dim);
		line-height: 1.75;
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
		max-width: 62ch;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.about-head {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: flex-start;
			gap: 1rem;
		}

		.avatar {
			width: 100px;
			height: 100px;
		}
	}
</style>
